🚀 Quick Start

Clone or download the project files
Open index.html in a modern browser
Allow microphone access when prompted
Start adding tasks with voice or keyboard!

📋 File Contents
1. index.html
Main HTML structure with semantic markup for accessibility.
2. css/styles.css
Modern styling with:

Glassmorphism design
Responsive layout
Smooth animations
Accessibility features

3. js/app.js
Core functionality including:

Web Speech API integration
Task management
Local storage
Error handling

4. README.md
Complete documentation with:

Setup instructions
Feature overview
Browser compatibility
Usage guide

5. package.json
Project metadata for easy deployment and sharing.
🎯 Features

Voice Recognition: Real-time speech-to-text conversion
Manual Input: Keyboard alternative for accessibility
Task Management: Add, complete, and delete tasks
Persistent Storage: Data saved locally
Responsive Design: Works on all devices
Modern UI: Clean, accessible interface

🌐 Browser Support

✅ Chrome/Chromium (Full support)
✅ Edge (Full support)
✅ Safari (Full support)
⚠️ Firefox (Manual input only)

📱 Mobile Ready
The app is fully responsive and works great on mobile devices, though voice recognition support varies by mobile browser.
🔧 Customization
Easy to customize:

Colors and themes in styles.css
Voice recognition settings in app.js
UI text and labels in index.html
